  "name": "Create social media posts from New blog post and send to LinkedIn",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Create social media posts from New blog post and send to LinkedIn",
  "category": "Marketing",
  "tags": [
    "n8n 2000 workflows",
    "slack",
